$ ./search_su2_odd_orbit_gks rank3-depth 500
SU2_ODD_ORBIT_RANK3_DEPTH maximum_power=500 words=1004004 \
    boundary_entries=3012012 minimum_corner=0 minimum_boundary=0 \
    result=PASS

The first scan enumerates the complete support-disjoint chamber by total
degree.  The second independently scans the rectangle 0<=p,q<=500 for all
four sign choices, checking the scalar corner and all three boundary
coefficients with arbitrary-precision integers.  These are cross-checks of
the uniform spectral-pair proof in Proposition 22H3N, not substitutes for
that proof.

5. Rank-three standard-orthant no-go diagnostic
------------------------------------------------
$ make -B -j1 analyze_su2_odd_orbit_rank3_cone
g++ -O2 -std=c++20 -Wall -Wextra -Wpedantic -Wconversion \
    -Wsign-conversion -Wshadow -Werror \
    analyze_su2_odd_orbit_rank3_cone.cpp \
    -o analyze_su2_odd_orbit_rank3_cone

$ ./analyze_su2_odd_orbit_rank3_cone
